Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,======================================== TEXT ========================================
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.62,0:00:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,請進
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.88,0:00:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,大小姐　
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.04,0:00:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,請問是這本嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.07,0:00:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.03,0:00:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.11,0:00:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,您是要用來做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.67,0:00:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,關於這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.61,0:02:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,小雲雀　
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.49,0:02:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,成績如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.42,0:02:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,也就普普通通
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.00,0:02:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼從明天起放暑假
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.42,0:02:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,在夏令營前請務必保重
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.25,0:02:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,夏令營前…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.67,0:02:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,以上　
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.68,0:02:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,第一學期結課
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.86,0:02:22.62,Title,,0,0,0,,{@\an8\fs60\fn方正综艺_GBK\c&HF1B368&\pos(644,446)}我們的暑假
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.98,0:02:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,轉啊轉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.99,0:02:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,等等牡丹
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.09,0:02:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,那樣亂轉的話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.69,0:02:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,小牡丹！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.28,0:02:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,烏…烏賊先生滿天轉…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.98,0:02:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我才說嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.64,0:02:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.06,0:02:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,總之…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.21,0:02:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,去那裡休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.67,0:02:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.40,0:02:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,垃圾如我　
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.40,0:02:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,竟不知天高地厚的亢奮起來…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.43,0:02:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,明天起就是暑假了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.91,0:03:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,想著可以和大家各種玩耍
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.74,0:03:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不知不覺就…軲轆軲轆轉起圈來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.23,0:03:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,太羞人了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.91,0:03:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,大家高興了都會轉起圈的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.51,0:03:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,轉啊轉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.78,0:03:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,好像也不那麼常見
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.73,0:03:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.87,0:03:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,是小蓮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.83,0:03:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,小蓮是你叫的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.46,0:03:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,小響也在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.13,0:03:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,所以說不要隨意叫小響…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.37,0:03:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你們在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.53,0:03:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,天氣微熱　小憩一番
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.75,0:03:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,小憩？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.01,0:03:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,是…是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.77,0:03:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,不介意的話　要去嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.78,0:03:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,哇 卡拉OK!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.85,0:03:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,卡拉OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.97,0:03:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,哼 昨天滿臉通紅的女店員
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.41,0:03:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,竟然厚臉皮的把這個送給了蓮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.23,0:03:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,想去我想去卡拉OK!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.19,0:04:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,機會難得　
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.46,0:04:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,那就恭敬不如從命了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.18,0:04:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.48,0:04:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,難不成！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.76,0:04:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,是擔心聽了我難聽歌聲　
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.58,0:04:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,耳朵會爛掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.20,0:04:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼可能！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.83,0:04:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你這傢伙心眼好壞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.72,0:04:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,都說我沒那麼想！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.20,0:04:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,只是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.66,0:04:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我…那個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.61,0:04:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,從未去過卡拉OK
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.68,0:04:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,真沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.98,0:04:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,就由我這個卡拉OK大師
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.85,0:04:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,響親自來指導你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.70,0:04:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,好呀 走啦走啦小雲雀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.07,0:04:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,一二一二一二
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.14,0:04:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{@\fn方正综艺_GBK\bord2\shad0\frz352.8\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H8D7FE1&\move(412,202,788,202,23,5945)\fax0.15\fay0.01}卡拉OK
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.62,0:05:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,響唱的真的好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.35,0:05:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,是的　
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.30,0:05:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,這旋律十分熟悉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.62,0:05:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,牡丹經常來卡拉OK嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.25,0:05:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,不是的　
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.33,0:05:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是第一次進卡拉OK包廂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.58,0:05:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,因為家裡有唱K設施　
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.01,0:05:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,偶爾會去用
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.33,0:05:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,設施…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.52,0:05:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,是的　
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.59,0:05:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,除此之外還有各種設施
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.80,0:05:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,請各位一定抽空來玩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.43,0:05:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,那就明天吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.51,0:05:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,明天？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.36,0:05:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 那明天去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.29,0:05:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,好的　
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.94,0:05:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,非常歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.43,0:05:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,也好啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.95,0:05:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,餵你們根本沒聽響唱歌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.41,0:05:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,來 下一首是你　
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.91,0:05:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,雲雀丘瑠璃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.80,0:06:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,這　這就輪到我了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.00,0:06:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,見…見笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.44,0:06:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,雲雀唱的超好聽！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.08,0:06:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼嘛　
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.81,0:06:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,這不是會唱麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.68,0:06:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,雲雀同學的嗓音十分動聽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.71,0:06:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.01,0:06:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我不太清楚近來的流行歌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.18,0:06:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,這是很久之前聽的一首…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.39,0:06:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,CD嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.95,0:06:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,不　
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.10,0:06:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,是母親邊打理庭園邊哼唱的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.67,0:06:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,剛剛查了一下歌詞才知道曲名
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.31,0:06:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,原來如此　
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.91,0:06:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,真的好棒　雲雀同學
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.63,0:06:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,謝…謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.27,0:06:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,接下來輪到我唱了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.70,0:06:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,花子同學　請加油
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.23,0:07:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,這是什麼　
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.08,0:07:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,耳朵要…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.08,0:07:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,牡丹撐住！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.96,0:07:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,這是麥的蜂鳴聲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.67,0:07:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,可她還沒唱　
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.09,0:07:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,離擴音器也很遠
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.62,0:07:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,果然還是不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.60,0:07:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,每次去卡拉OK　
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.58,0:07:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我拿起話筒時一定會發出刺耳聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.75,0:07:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,各位好呀　齊聚一堂真熱鬧呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.81,0:07:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,貓尾草！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.11,0:07:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.42,0:07:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,暫時要見不到大家了　來道個別
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.81,0:07:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,道別？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.27,0:07:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,暑假期間我要去檢查身體異常
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.19,0:07:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,就像住院體檢一樣對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.38,0:07:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,貓了個尾草
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.33,0:07:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼作為餞別禮 獻唱一曲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.50,0:07:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,貓尾草 貓尾草 貓尾草
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.59,0:07:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\an8}貓貓貓貓尾草高興
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.23,0:08:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,貓貓貓貓尾…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.51,0:08:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,停下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.07,0:08:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,貓貓貓貓尾 加時
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.67,0:08:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,不加好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.10,0:08:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,「貓貓貓尾貓尾」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.33,0:08:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,貓尾草就這樣表演了精彩的Rap
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.34,0:08:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,卡拉OK大會就這樣結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.51,0:08:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,蟬先生還在叫呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.22,0:08:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,又來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.09,0:08:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.65,0:08:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,昨天卡拉OK結束之後
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.09,0:08:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,貓尾草的Rap就一直在腦海裡打轉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.47,0:08:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,貓貓貓尾貓尾的那首歌？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.18,0:08:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,快停下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.51,0:08:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,又會想起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.07,0:08:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,那就用其他能停留在耳朵裡的歌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.45,0:08:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,來忘記貓尾草的歌怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.63,0:08:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,比如說？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.07,0:08:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.71,0:08:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,CM裡的「好吃好吃」之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.25,0:08:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,這次那個反而會被記住
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.35,0:09:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,那就「紅黴青黴黑黴全都解決掉」CM的歌呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.10,0:09:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你還來啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.61,0:09:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,但是果然還是貓貓貓尾貓尾對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.98,0:09:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,所以說啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.28,0:09:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.43,0:09:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.85,0:09:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,感覺看到我的臉後有些害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.78,0:09:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我的表情真的那麼可怕嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.25,0:09:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有 是平常的小雲雀哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.27,0:09:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎 那又是為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.30,0:09:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,這全都是貓尾草的Rap的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.00,0:09:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,是大海
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.03,0:10:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.82,0:10:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,小雲雀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.67,0:10:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,快看快看 螃蟹 是螃蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.48,0:10:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我咬
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.62,0:10:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,花子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.07,0:10:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,海鷗海鷗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.41,0:10:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,話說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.83,0:10:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,真是嚇了一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.62,0:10:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,這些竟然全部都是人造的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.48,0:10:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,是妹妹為了不能去海水浴的我拜託別人做的設施
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.37,0:10:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,實在是太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.93,0:10:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,所以說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.90,0:10:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,能邀請大家真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.97,0:10:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,牡丹 你有妹妹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.91,0:10:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,和耗錢費事如路邊石子一般的我不同
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.78,0:10:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,妹妹運動萬能而且很開朗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.60,0:10:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.68,0:11:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,釣到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.97,0:11:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,裡面也和真的大海一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.87,0:11:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,比賽誰先到那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.04,0:11:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.65,0:11:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,好痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.51,0:11:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.47,0:11:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,得手了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.26,0:11:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.38,0:11:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,意識恢復了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.50,0:11:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,響到底…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.02,0:11:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你在潛水的時候失去意識了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.38,0:11:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,蓮同學的應急措施真是太科學了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.66,0:11:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.90,0:11:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,應急措施
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.88,0:11:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,難道說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.08,0:11:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,喂不要睡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.64,0:11:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,好球
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.69,0:11:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,是安打
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.54,0:11:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,賽點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.88,0:12:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,然後大家和醒過來的蓮同學一起玩了切西瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.97,0:12:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,寫下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.50,0:12:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,接下來是鎮上的祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.73,0:12:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.93,0:12:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我出發了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.41,0:12:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{@\an7\fs60\fn方正康体_GBK\bord6\shad0\3c&HC6E0F7&\pos(342.667,188.667)}大型煙花大會
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.41,0:12:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{@\an7\fs60\fn方正康体_GBK\c&H4BD8FB&\bord2\shad0\3c&H5585DD&\pos(342.667,188.667)}大型煙花大會
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.92,0:13:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.41,0:13:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,花子 這不是正好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.36,0:13:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,今天只掉到了河裡一次
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.15,0:13:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,果然掉河了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.49,0:13:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,那走散的話就在這裡集合
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.61,0:13:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,說的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.93,0:13:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,那就趕快去逛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.97,0:13:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼時候買的烏賊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.38,0:13:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{@\fr270\bord4\fn@DFKanTeiRyu-W11\pos(252,108)\3c&H1953D7&}蘋果糖
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.38,0:13:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{@\fr270\fn@DFKanTeiRyu-W11\c&H144ADF&\pos(252,108)\3c&H76CCF7&}蘋果糖
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.69,0:14:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{@\fs28\b1\c&H0C0AE9&\3c&H4AC0F9&\bord3\frz8.638\fax-0.15\pos(774,162)}棉花糖
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.08,0:14:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{@\an1\bord3\fax-0.46\fn@方正大黑_GBK\fs23\c&H0539B4&\3c&H0638C3&\frz-90\pos(726.666,173.333)}巧克力香蕉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.08,0:14:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{@\an1\fax-0.46\fn@方正大黑_GBK\fs23\c&H0539B4&\3c&H0BC6F2&\frz-90\pos(726.666,173.333)}巧克力香蕉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.86,0:14:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,盯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.70,0:14:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,散開 散開
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.51,0:14:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.10,0:14:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{@\c&H0D1DA6&\3c&H7FCBFD&\bord2\fn@方正粗圆_GBK\fr270\fs30\pos(628,120)}章魚燒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.25,0:14:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,小雲雀她們呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.56,0:14:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,難道說我們走散了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.98,0:14:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,那就去集合的地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.30,0:14:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,說的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.50,0:14:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,接下來去吃那個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.93,0:14:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,已經吃夠多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.23,0:14:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,起碼想成功一次
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.04,0:14:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.10,0:14:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.58,0:14:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,響和花小泉同學呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.05,0:15:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,她們人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.25,0:15:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,響明明都聽她們的在這裡等了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.25,0:15:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,剛纔的是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.69,0:15:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,貓尾草
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.36,0:15:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,等
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.72,0:15:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,會走散的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.20,0:15:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,都叫你等了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.83,0:15:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,貓尾草
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.08,0:15:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.18,0:15:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,不要管那傢伙不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.97,0:15:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,快點回去正門…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.84,0:15:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\an8}小響 這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.85,0:15:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡 聽人說話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.94,0:15:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,別…別留下我一個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.70,0:15:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,晚上的學校原來是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.01,0:15:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我第一次進來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.78,0:15:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,說的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.03,0:15:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,好 回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.34,0:15:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,立刻回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.57,0:16:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,剛纔好像傳來了響的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.62,0:16:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,從哪來的？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.06,0:16:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,那邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.09,0:16:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.37,0:16:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.75,0:16:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,可能會出現什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.69,0:16:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,小響 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.00,0:16:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,說什麼呢  以為我會害怕就大錯特錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.25,0:16:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,咦  小響很害怕嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.48,0:16:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,所以說響怎麼會害怕…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.59,0:16:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.83,0:16:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,那去看看那邊的教室吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.50,0:16:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,等下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.30,0:16:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,是惡靈乾的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.38,0:16:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,點不亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.83,0:16:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,很好這樣就…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.39,0:16:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,好多大叔的人像啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.38,0:16:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.24,0:17:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{@\bord0\xshad5\yshad-3\an8\fn楷体\b1\c&HE3CFCC&\4c&H503A2F&\pos(640,86.667)}初代校長 堀川照三
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.01,0:17:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,好像是校長的像呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.61,0:17:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,有那麼多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.42,0:17:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,大家好像都在笑好可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.05,0:17:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.51,0:17:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,響也不知道哪裡可愛了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.51,0:17:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你看再和你打招呼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.73,0:17:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\an8}快從這裡出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.75,0:17:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,這到底是？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.50,0:17:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,學園祭的小道具吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.52,0:17:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,這個顴骨到下顎骨的肌肉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.50,0:17:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,說明了他幸福的成長了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.44,0:17:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,夠了 回大門吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.11,0:17:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,花子她們一定也在那
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.41,0:17:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,有人在唱歌嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.08,0:17:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.98,0:17:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你聽到了什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.03,0:17:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,那種令人懷唸的 觸動人心的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.04,0:17:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,有點害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.63,0:18:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,第七代校長是女性呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.44,0:18:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,瞭解歷代校長有什麼用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.89,0:18:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,快點回到原來的正門
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.53,0:18:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,這是什麼聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.74,0:18:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我什麼都沒聽到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.60,0:18:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,不聽到了 肯定聽到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.33,0:18:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,難道是校長們在說話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.50,0:18:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,拜託你不要說這種話了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.54,0:18:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,這個歌聲 有點可怕還感覺心裡癢癢的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.03,0:18:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,說到盔甲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.63,0:18:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,有個傳說是說一套渴望血的盔甲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.33,0:18:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,會襲擊來到城裡的觀光客
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.63,0:18:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,到了晚上那盔甲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.67,0:18:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,拿著沾滿被襲擊客人血的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.20,0:18:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,高興地數著「一件 兩件」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.32,0:18:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,停停停
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.25,0:18:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,這個不是這個梗的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.93,0:18:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我也聽說過這樣的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.92,0:19:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,戰國時代戰敗陣亡的山梨縣出身武士的盔甲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.72,0:19:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,慢慢站起來說到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.73,0:19:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,桃子李子都是桃科
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.73,0:19:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{@\an7\fs30}※ 日本繞口令
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.18,0:19:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,都是桃科…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.98,0:19:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,都是桃桃科
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.41,0:19:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,桃子貓尾…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.86,0:19:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,貓尾貓尾尾
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.66,0:19:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,貓貓貓貓貓尾草
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.41,0:19:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\an8}別說了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.43,0:19:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,難道是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.41,0:19:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,這是貓尾草的歌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.71,0:19:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,貓尾草
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.82,0:19:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\an8}等一下 不要丟下響
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.58,0:19:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,是這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.04,0:19:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,花子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.59,0:19:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,各位
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.50,0:19:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,這歌是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.16,0:19:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,是貓尾草
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.36,0:19:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,真的要進去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.74,0:19:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,走
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.80,0:20:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.76,0:20:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼全都散架了卻能聽見貓尾草的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.64,0:20:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,這是為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.10,0:20:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿咻
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.20,0:20:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,惡靈退散惡靈退散
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.92,0:20:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,等下…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.23,0:20:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,牡丹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.45,0:20:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,太狡猾了 響也…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.73,0:20:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,腳腳腳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.11,0:20:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,奔跑的腳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.59,0:20:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,說到散架 我聽說…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.78,0:20:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,大約十年前  某國家的牧羊人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.90,0:20:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.40,0:20:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,腳 貓尾草的腳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.87,0:20:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,每天晚上一個人吃火鍋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.32,0:20:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,火鍋的話  是冬天嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.06,0:20:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,咱現在說點有用的成嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.93,0:20:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,某一天發現鍋裡肉都吃完了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.84,0:20:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定是貪吃鬼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.47,0:21:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,蓮 響不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.40,0:21:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,別唱了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.11,0:21:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,那到底是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.60,0:21:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,明明散架了還唱Rap
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.46,0:21:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,算了 放棄思考了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.34,0:21:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,不過 很開心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.53,0:21:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.52,0:21:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,是個不錯的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.90,0:21:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
